    <r3d:remarks>Odum Dataverse is covered by Thomson Reuters Data Citation Index. The Odum Institute houses one of the oldest and largest catalogs of machine-readable data in the United States. The Data Archive has an extensive collection of U.S. Census data, including one of the most comprehensive holdings for 1970 Census files. It also contains data from the North Carolina State Data Center, National Center for Health Statistics and Harris Polls. Almost all of the data holdings are available online in the Odum Dataverse.</r3d:remarks>
